<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="here/main_template/macros/master">
      
<head>
    <metal:css fill-slot="css_slot">
    </metal:css>
</head>

<body>
<metal:main fill-slot="main">

<h1>Plone for <span tal:replace="here/Title">NGOs</span></h1>

<p class="discreet"
   style="float:right; width: 128px; margin: 0 0 1em 1em; text-align: center" tal:condition="exists: here/responsible.jpg">
    <img tal:replace="structure here/responsible.jpg/image_thumb" /><br />
    <span tal:replace="here/responsible.jpg/Description"></span>
</p>
<p class="documentDescription" tal:content="here/Description">Desc</p>

<div class="visualClear"><!-- --></div>


    <h2>Case Studies</h2>
<tal:block repeat="case python:here.portal_catalog(Type='Case Study', size_limit=2), path='/'.join(here.getPhysicalPath())">
  <div style="width: 47%; float: left; margin: 0 1em 1em 0;">
    <h3 tal:content="case/Title">Case study 1</h3>
    <p tal:content="case/Description">Description goes here</p>
    <p><a tal:attributes="href case/getURL">Read more...</a></p>
   </div>
</tal:block>
<div class="visualClear"><!-- --></div>

<div style="width: 47%; float: left; margin: 0 1em 1em 0;">

    <h2>References</h2>

    <p>What organizations are are running Plone in this sector?</p>
    <p>
        <a href="">See all&hellip;</a>
    </p>
</div>

<div style="width: 47%; float: left">
    <h2>News</h2>

    <ul>
        <li><a href="">Some announcement</a> <span class="discreet">25.01.2006</span></li>
        <li><a href="">Another announcement</a> <span class="discreet">25.01.2006</span></li>
    </ul>

    <p><a href="news" style="float: right">Read all&hellip;</a></p>
</div>

<div class="visualClear"><!-- --></div>

</metal:main>
</body>
</html>

